name: On the Range Golf sports art print
description:
The On the Range Golf art print is available in 3 sizes: 10" tall, 14" tall, and 18" tall.

 They are printed on premium heavy weight giclee paper with a slight texture. Each print has 1" of white paper at the top and bottom and extra white on the sides, to accommodate my hand signature and stamp. 

Shipped flat in heavy cardboard mailer and sealed in cellophane sleeve.

Prints typically take 4-7 business days to arrive to customer.
